From: Aaron Liu <aaron.liu@amd.com>
Date: Tue, 15 Oct 2019 16:47:44 +0800
Subject: drm/amdgpu: enable TMZ bit in sdma copy pkt for sdma v4
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: b7c163fe910fd38000f85b871bf25b120282e702
Patch-mainline: v5.8-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322

Enable sdma TMZ mode via setting TMZ bit in sdma copy pkt
for sdma v4

Signed-off-by: Aaron Liu <aaron.liu@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Christian KÃ¶nig <christian.koenig@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Huang Rui <ray.huang@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/sdma_v4_0.c | 3 ++-
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/sdma_v4_0.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/sdma_v4_0.c
index 40d205a14e44..ebd723a0bcfc 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/sdma_v4_0.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/sdma_v4_0.c
@@ -2462,7 +2462,8 @@ static void sdma_v4_0_emit_copy_buffer(struct amdgpu_ib *ib,
 				       bool tmz)
 {
 	ib->ptr[ib->length_dw++] = SDMA_PKT_HEADER_OP(SDMA_OP_COPY) |
-		SDMA_PKT_HEADER_SUB_OP(SDMA_SUBOP_COPY_LINEAR);
+		SDMA_PKT_HEADER_SUB_OP(SDMA_SUBOP_COPY_LINEAR) |
+		SDMA_PKT_COPY_LINEAR_HEADER_TMZ(tmz ? 1 : 0);
 	ib->ptr[ib->length_dw++] = byte_count - 1;
 	ib->ptr[ib->length_dw++] = 0; /* src/dst endian swap */
 	ib->ptr[ib->length_dw++] = lower_32_bits(src_offset);
